channel.title: Runescape Private Server Online Problem
channel.description:
Hello there. I am a owner of a runescape private server called Runecient and the problem is that I am trying to connect online and it says that the server has been updated and but I talk to my friend (There's only 2 owners of this server.) and he never made a update of anything and there may have 1 file that is missing.
I have tried to run a run.bat but it has never worked. Please help me. :/
By the way, if you're interest in joining my server, please do so. It's a 317 server. :)
www.runecient.com
